            <StackLayout>
                <Label Text="Interests" FontSize="16" FontAttributes="Bold"/>
                <Label Text="Apart from studying, I enjoy being outdoors. In the winter, I love to go iceskating, and someday I would take a trip to Austria, because I have always wanted to go on a skiing vacation.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
