                    I love to help my family with their computer problems, because I like lending a hand when someone needs it. I've, among other things, helped my grandmothers a lot with their small IT and software troubles.&lt;br/&gt;" 
                    TextType="Html"/>

                <Label Text="Personal skills" FontSize="16" FontAttributes="Bold"/>
                <Label Text="I'm as a person forthcoming, flexible and hard working. I bring a good mood, great humor and a positive approach to the working day. 
