                       &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Me as a person:" TextType="Html" />
                <StackLayout Padding="15,0,15,0">
                    <Label Text="&#x2022; Devoted, forthcoming and a quick learner." />
                    <Label Text="&#x2022; Smiling, mature and always in a good mood, which gives a lot of energy to a busy working day." />
                    <Label Text="&#x2022; Always ready to give all I've got and do my job to satisfaction." />
                    <Label Text="&#x2022; Determined, good to prioritization and enterprising." />
                    <Label Text="&#x2022; Good at both cooperation and working independent." />
                </StackLayout>
                <Label Text="I find programming so fascinating, I love learning new things and I'm looking forward to making it a part of my everyday life. Before I began at my first semester, I took the course 'JavaScript Fundamentals ES6 for beginners' at udemy.com, which I found very exciting and educative." 
                    TextType="Html" />
            </StackLayout>
